<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.1.7">
<l>ōṭāta vāḷariyi ṉuruvāki yiraṇiyaṉai</l>
<l>vāṭāta vaḷḷukirāl piḷantaḷainta mālatiṭam</l>
<l>ēṭēṟu peruñcelvat teḻilmaṟaiyōr nāṅkaitaṉṉuḷ</l>
<l>cēṭēṟu poḻiltaḻuvu tiruttēva ṉārtokaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place for Māl who, being in the form of an invincible man-lion,</l>
<l>Having split Hiraṇya with his sharp, unfailing claws, twisted [them],</l>
<l>Is Tiruttēvaṉārtokai in Nāṅkai, embraced by beautiful groves,</l>
<l>With experts in the Vedas, the beauty of whose great [wealth of] learning</l>
<l rend="indent">appears on palm-leaves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
